casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Locke.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Locke (1988), 40 Ohio St. 3d 605.]

(No. D.R. 88-9 Submitted December 2, 1988 Decided December 29, 1988.)

The resignation of Thomas E. Locke as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
